title: Otter Browser 0.9.10 Beta 10 - Crackingpatching

Follow Us:

[b]Description:[/b]
Otter Browser & nbsp; - is a browser that tries to recreate the best aspects of classical Opera 12.x versions and user interface using Qt5 engine. Overall I was pleased with the program, quick start, easy to operate, has Russian support, all sites are displayed correctly in the whole of the new special nothing. 
The draft (as of this writing) is a stage of the Alpha test, so if you have any problems, bugs, bugs, just notes, can write on the official website for developers, with your help, they may be able to improve your browser. 
Not yet published the final version, I'll lay out a portable version Otter Browser, while at the same official site, you can download the installation files if it's someone you need. In the security settings, you will be able to put private mode, you can change the tracking parameters. In the Tools section, subsection Block content, as I understand it, we are talking about the Adblock, only I could not configure it, do not quite understand how it works, so advertising is displayed everywhere. 
In general, there is nothing to tell me more about the program, if you have anything to add, please comment, I hope together we can help developers, all the luck. 

Developer: bajasoft, emdek 
License: FreeWare 
Language: English + Multi 
OS: Windows
